query:
SELECT MIN(n.name) AS member_in_charnamed_american_movie, MIN(n.name) AS a1
FROM sampled_cast_info_4 AS ci,
   sampled_company_name_4 AS cn,
   sampled_keyword_4 AS k,
   sampled_movie_companies_4 AS mc,
   sampled_movie_keyword_4 AS mk,
   sampled_name_4 AS n,
   sampled_title_4 AS t
WHERE n.id = ci.person_id
AND ci.movie_id = t.id
AND t.id = mk.movie_id
AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
AND t.id = mc.movie_id
AND mc.company_id = cn.id
AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation'
AND n.name LIKE 'H%';
plan_content: /*+  SeqScan(k) IndexScan(mk keyword_id_movie_keyword_4) IndexOnlyScan(t sampled_title_4_pkey) IndexScan(ci movie_id_cast_info_4) IndexScan(n sampled_name_4_pkey) IndexScan(mc movie_id_movie_companies_4) IndexScan(cn sampled_company_name_4_pkey) NestLoop(k mk) NestLoop(k mk t) NestLoop(k mk t ci) NestLoop(k mk t ci n) NestLoop(k mk t ci n mc) NestLoop(k mk t ci n mc cn) Leading(((((((k mk) t) ci) n) mc) cn)) */

FROM sampled_cast_info_4 AS ci,
   sampled_company_name_4 AS cn,
   sampled_keyword_4 AS k,
   sampled_movie_companies_4 AS mc,
   sampled_movie_keyword_4 AS mk,
   sampled_name_4 AS n,
   sampled_title_4 AS t
WHERE n.id = ci.person_id
AND ci.movie_id = t.id
AND t.id = mk.movie_id
AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
AND t.id = mc.movie_id
AND mc.company_id = cn.id
AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
AND k.keyword = 'sequel'
AND n.name LIKE 'A%';
plan_content: /*+  SeqScan(k) IndexScan(mk keyword_id_movie_keyword_4) IndexOnlyScan(t sampled_title_4_pkey) IndexScan(ci movie_id_cast_info_4) IndexScan(n sampled_name_4_pkey) IndexScan(mc movie_id_movie_companies_4) IndexScan(cn sampled_company_name_4_pkey) NestLoop(k mk) NestLoop(k mk t) NestLoop(k mk t ci) NestLoop(k mk t ci n) NestLoop(k mk t ci n mc) NestLoop(k mk t ci n mc cn) Leading(((((((k mk) t) ci) n) mc) cn)) */
